This  directory  contains  the  sources of the Oberon  System  version 4 for
Ceres-2  Workstations.  They replace the earlier version 1 sources described
in the book "Project Oberon" from N.  Wirth & J.  Gutknecht.

In version 2 Text-Elements  were introduced and the main visible  difference
between version 2 and version 4 is "Edit", the document  editor,  previously
called "Write" in version 2

For more information about the differences  between version 2 and version 4,
read the Postscript file 00_V4.docu.ps in this directory.



